{"info": {"author": "Mike Monteith", "author_email": "<mike.monteith@nhs.net>", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": [], "description": "# Wagtail NHS.UK frontend\n\nA wagtail implementation of the [NHS frontend v3.0.4](https://github.com/nhsuk/nhsuk-frontend) standard components.\n\n## Installation\n\nInstall the pypi package\n```\npip install wagtail-nhsuk-frontend\n```\n\nAdd to your `INSTALLED_APPS` in wagtail settings\n```python\nINSTALLED_APPS = [\n  ...\n\n  'wagtailnhsukfrontend',\n\n  ...\n]\n```\n\nUse blocks in your streamfields\n```python\nfrom wagtail.admin.edit_handlers import FieldPanel, StreamFieldPanel\nfrom wagtail.core.models import Page\nfrom wagtail.core.fields import StreamField\n\nfrom wagtailnhsukfrontend.blocks import ActionLinkBlock, WarningCalloutBlock\n\nclass HomePage(Page):\n  body = StreamField([\n      # Include any of the blocks you want to use.\n      ('action_link', ActionLinkBlock()),\n      ('callout', WarningCalloutBlock()),\n  ])\n\n  content_panels = Page.content_panels + [\n      StreamFieldPanel('body'),\n  ]\n```\n\nUse templatetags\n```django\n{% load nhsukfrontend_tags %}\n\n<html>\n...\n<body>\n  {% breadcrumb %}\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\nUse template includes\n```django\n{% include 'wagtailnhsukfrontend/header.html' with show_search=True %}\n```\n\nSee the [component documentation](./docs/components/) for a list of components you can use.\n\nInclude the CSS in your base template\n```html\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"{% static 'wagtailnhsukfrontend/css/wagtail-nhsuk-frontend.min.css' %}\">\n```\n\nInclude the Javascript in your base template\n```html\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"{% static 'wagtailnhsukfrontend/js/nhsuk-3.0.4.min.js' %}\" defer></script>\n```\n\n## Contributing \n\nSee the [contributing documentation](./docs/contributing.md) to run the application locally and contribute changes.\n\n## Further reading\n\nSee more [documentation](./docs/)", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/nhsuk/wagtail-nhsuk-frontend", "keywords": "", "license": "", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "wagtail-nhsuk-frontend", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/wagtail-nhsuk-frontend/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/wagtail-nhsuk-frontend/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/nhsuk/wagtail-nhsuk-frontend"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/wagtail-nhsuk-frontend/0.4.2/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": "", "summary": "NHSUK Frontend Styles for Wagtail", "version": "0.4.2", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>Wagtail NHS.UK frontend</h1>\n<p>A wagtail implementation of the <a href=\"https://github.com/nhsuk/nhsuk-frontend\" rel=\"nofollow\">NHS frontend v3.0.4</a> standard components.</p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Install the pypi package</p>\n<pre><code>pip install wagtail-nhsuk-frontend\n</code></pre>\n<p>Add to your <code>INSTALLED_APPS</code> in wagtail settings</p>\n<pre><span class=\"n\">INSTALLED_APPS</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">...</span>\n\n  <span class=\"s1\">'wagtailnhsukfrontend'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n\n  <span class=\"o\">...</span>\n<span class=\"p\">]</span>\n</pre>\n<p>Use blocks in your streamfields</p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">wagtail.admin.edit_handlers</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">FieldPanel</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">StreamFieldPanel</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">wagtail.core.models</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Page</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">wagtail.core.fields</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">StreamField</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">wagtailnhsukfrontend.blocks</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">ActionLinkBlock</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">WarningCalloutBlock</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\">HomePage</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Page</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">body</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">StreamField</span><span class=\"p\">([</span>\n      <span class=\"c1\"># Include any of the blocks you want to use.</span>\n      <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'action_link'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">ActionLinkBlock</span><span class=\"p\">()),</span>\n      <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'callout'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">WarningCalloutBlock</span><span class=\"p\">()),</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">])</span>\n\n  <span class=\"n\">content_panels</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Page</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">content_panels</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">StreamFieldPanel</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'body'</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">]</span>\n</pre>\n<p>Use templatetags</p>\n<pre><span class=\"cp\">{%</span> <span class=\"k\">load</span> <span class=\"nv\">nhsukfrontend_tags</span> <span class=\"cp\">%}</span><span class=\"x\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"x\">&lt;html&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"x\">...</span>\n<span class=\"x\">&lt;body&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"x\">  </span><span class=\"cp\">{%</span> <span class=\"k\">breadcrumb</span> <span class=\"cp\">%}</span><span class=\"x\"></span>\n<span class=\"x\">&lt;/body&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"x\">&lt;/html&gt;</span>\n</pre>\n<p>Use template includes</p>\n<pre><span class=\"cp\">{%</span> <span class=\"k\">include</span> <span class=\"s1\">'wagtailnhsukfrontend/header.html'</span> <span class=\"k\">with</span> <span class=\"nv\">show_search</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kp\">True</span> <span class=\"cp\">%}</span><span class=\"x\"></span>\n</pre>\n<p>See the <a href=\"./docs/components/\" rel=\"nofollow\">component documentation</a> for a list of components you can use.</p>\n<p>Include the CSS in your base template</p>\n<pre>  <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nt\">link</span> <span class=\"na\">rel</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">\"stylesheet\"</span> <span class=\"na\">type</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">\"text/css\"</span> <span class=\"na\">href</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">\"{% static 'wagtailnhsukfrontend/css/wagtail-nhsuk-frontend.min.css' %}\"</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</pre>\n<p>Include the Javascript in your base template</p>\n<pre>  <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nt\">script</span> <span class=\"na\">type</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">\"text/javascript\"</span> <span class=\"na\">src</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">\"{% static 'wagtailnhsukfrontend/js/nhsuk-3.0.4.min.js' %}\"</span> <span class=\"na\">defer</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"nt\">script</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</pre>\n<h2>Contributing</h2>\n<p>See the <a href=\"./docs/contributing.md\" rel=\"nofollow\">contributing documentation</a> to run the application locally and contribute changes.</p>\n<h2>Further reading</h2>\n<p>See more <a href=\"./docs/\" rel=\"nofollow\">documentation</a></p>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 7024844, "releases": {"0.1.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "804728d589d84facc14478f1b31f3458", "sha256": "df036725790ca804a47895c32079ac146f6876aaddec29fe83cead6f2d6aa740"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "wagtail-nhsuk-frontend-0.1.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "804728d589d84facc14478f1b31f3458", "pa